    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The vehicle exhibits excellent mechanical integrity, with a recently refreshed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under load. Power is delivered through a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit stability. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering precise feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. Well-maintained and mechanically sound, this M3 delivers the raw, analog performance expected of this legendary chassis.",
