    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable companion and remains in impressive shape both inside and out. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. The interior is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats are firm and free of tears, while the dashboard and electronics\u2014including the premium audio system and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, it is in excellent working order with a documented service history, including a recent transmission flush and a fresh set of tires installed last season. It handles beautifully with no unusual noises or vibrations, offering a smooth and confident driving experience. This is a solid, well-cared-for car ready for its next chapter.",
