      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS system serviced and rod bearings replaced as preventative measures. Power is delivered through a 3.62 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction out of corners. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates to address common floor pan fatigue. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with an enthusiast-driven life, the suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and crisp turn-in. A mechanically dialed-in machine for the purist.",
